== UBUZIBWA BWITE ==
'''ZANINKA''' Amazina ye nyakuri ni '''Mukarubayiza Drocella'''. Ni umubyeyi w'imyaka 60 y'amavuko akaba afite ndetse abana 6 , abakobwa 3 n'abahungu 3 hamwe n'abuzukuru 6, umukuru muribo afite imyaka 15 y'amavuko. Uyu ni umukinnyi wo mu ikinamico Musekeweya ndtse nizindi nyinshi harimo iyitwa "intabwe idasobanya" kuko yatangiye gukina ikinamico kuva kera.

